nodes.bodyText:
We should add the base path to a variable and then reference it throughout:
{{$slackPath := "/opennms/notifd/slack/" -}}

org.opennms.netmgt.notifd.slack.username={{getv (print $slackPath "userName") "none"}}

The print above concatenates the variable and string to form the full path.

